channel.title: [317] Server Base [/317]
channel.description:
Does anyone know of a good working base with some of following features:
When I say base I mean a place with some some simple commands and maybe a bank. No preset npc autospawns or anything.
Features:
Semi 100% Working Skills. Working animations (spells, fighting, some monsters) Simple commands that normal moparscape client has.
Ty for anyone who can find. Also a client with ip changer would be nice.
